description: Relax on the largest private secluded balcony in Riverfront Condos! Non-owner occupied short term rental eligible (NOO STR) AIRBNB. $40k+ year rental potential. Turn key - being sold fully furnished. Located only a few blocks from First Horizon Park and Germantown. Walkable to Broadway, Nissan Stadium. Tons of new developments in the area. Pool. Laundry Facility. Fitness Room. Covered parking. Water is included in HOA. This unit is located in the smallest building at the entrance.
